describedby="caption-attachment-3827991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg" alt="消防员继续扑灭洛杉矶帕利塞兹大火" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827991" class="wp-caption-text">消防队员继续与洛杉矶帕利塞兹大火作斗争。图片来源：CAL FIRE 的官方 Flickr 帐户/讲义/Anadolu，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>野火导致许多名人不得不撤离家园，其中一些人完全失去了家园，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heroes-star-milo-ventimiglia-chokes-up-after-watching-house-burn-down-in-la-wildfires-your-heart-just-breaks-3827763"><i>《英雄》</i>明星米洛·文堤米利亚</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-shares-footage-of-her-home-after-it-burned-down-in-la-wildfires-it-feels-like-my-heart-has-shattered-into-a-million-pieces-3827785">帕丽斯·希尔顿</a>（此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">发起了一项基金来帮助流离失所的家庭</a>）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/la-fires-mel-gibsons-says-his-house-burned-down-while-he-was-away-recording-joe-rogans-podcast-3828010">梅尔·吉布森</a>（他说自己的房子被烧毁了）当时他正在与乔·罗根一起录制播客。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">娱乐界的许多人对这些可怕的事件做出了反应</a>。昨天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">Charli XCX 敦促服装品牌向受火灾影响的人们捐款</a>。</p><p>已宣布为火灾受害者举办一场慈善音乐会。据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/los-angeles-fire-benefit-concert-fireaid-intuit-dome-1235874288/"><i>Billboard</i></a>报道，这场被称为“FireAid”的活动被描述为“音乐与团结之夜”，将于 1 月 30 日在洛杉矶 Intuit Dome 举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tyler-perry-hits-out-at-appalling-insurance-companies-pure-greed-amid-la-wildfires-destruction-3828515">泰勒·佩里 (Tyler Perry) 在洛杉矶山火破坏中猛烈抨击保险公司“令人震惊”的“纯粹贪婪”，</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
