and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔·萨特里亚尼和库尔特·科本。图片来源：Daniel Knighton 和 Jeff Kravitz，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Joe-Satriani-and-Kurt-Cobain.-Credit-Daniel-Knighton-and-Jeff-Kravitz-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Joe Satriani 公开了<a href="/artists/Kurt-Cobain">Kurt Cobain</a>的吉他演奏，并表示这位<a href="/artists/Nirvana">Nirvana</a>主唱在演奏斧头方面“非常出色”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/nirvanas-nevermind-at-30-a-track-by-track-guide-dave-grohl-st-vincent-lorde-3048697">Nirvana 30 岁时的《Nevermind》：来自您最喜爱的音乐家的逐首曲目指南</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/features/joe-satriani-kurt-cobain-good-guitarist" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>经典摇滚杂志</em></a>2025 年 1 月号的采访中，Satraini 在成为吉他偶像之前曾担任吉他教练，并教授过 Steve Vai、Larry LaLonde、Rick Hunolt、Kirk Hammett 等人，安迪·蒂蒙斯 (Andy Timmons)、查理·亨特 (Charlie Hunter) 等人讨论了《Smells Like Teen Spirit》的热门制作人，并表示他“对那些 Nirvana 唱片非常满意”。</p><p>然后他把注意力集中在柯本身上，并补充说这位传奇主唱“是一位伟大的吉他手”。</p><p> “你回去看看 Nirvana 的剪辑，你会发现这个家伙正在演奏他应该演奏的一切。他没有看自己在演奏什么，所以显然他真的很了解这种乐器，”他告诉该出版物。 “而且他正在与有史以来最伟大的鼓手之一 [<a href="/artists/Dave-Grohl">戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl</a> )] 一起演奏，所以如果他不是一名优秀的吉他手，那是行不通的。” </p><figure id="attachment_3828507" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828507" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828507" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing.jpg" alt="Nirvana 的 Kurt Cobain 在 MTV Live and Loud 期间进行现场表演：Nirvana 现场表演 - 1993 年 12 月在美国华盛顿州西雅图的 28 号码头。 （摄影：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic, Inc）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Kurt-Cobain-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828507" class="wp-caption-text"> Nirvana 乐队的库尔特·科本 (Kurt Cobain) 在 MTV Live and Loud 期间进行现场表演：Nirvana 现场表演 – 1993 年 12 月，美国华盛顿州西雅图 28 号码头。 （摄影：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic, Inc）</figcaption></figure><p>其他消息方面，Satriani 的专辑《G3 Reunion Live》（由吉他手 Vai 和 Eric Johnson 主演）将于 1 月 31 日通过 EarMUSIC 发行。 G3 是 Satriani 组织的一场音乐会巡演，由他和另外两位吉他手参加。</p><p>这张专辑标志着他们超过 25 年的现场专辑，其中包括三人组中每个人的“完整专辑长度的集合”以及“强大的吉他三人组的额外即兴素材”（来自<a href="https://loudwire.com/joe-satriani-thinks-kurt-cobain-great-guitarist/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Loudwire</em></a> ）。您可以<a href="https://g3reunionlive.lnk.to/Album" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预订。</p><p>在其他地方，Satriani 和 Vai 联手创建了 Satchvai Band，并计划于今年夏天开始 2025 年英国和欧洲巡演。查看下面的完整日期列表并访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsatchvai-band-featuring-joe-satriani-and-tickets%2Fartist%2F5518294" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DExZGc0tuAO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.