oads/2025/01/Madlib.-Credit-Richard-Bord-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Madlib.-Credit-Richard-Bord-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Madlib.-Credit-Richard-Bord-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madlib">马德利布</a>发起了一项筹款活动，帮助他和他的家人在加州<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">野火</a>中失去了洛杉矶的家、数十年的音乐和设备后“重建”。</p><p>制片人团队在 Instagram 上发出呼吁，请求捐款帮助 Madlib（真名小奥蒂斯·杰克逊·小奥蒂斯·杰克逊）和他的家人。在毁灭性的洛杉矶大火中失去了他们的家、几十年的音乐和设备，”它写道。</p><p> “您的捐款，无论金额多少，都将帮助 Madlib 和他的家人重建并继续创作感动许多人的音乐。您的捐款 100% 均可免税，并将直接捐给 Madlib 及其家人。预先感谢您的爱、祈祷和支持。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DExf4kMJR-7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-r